name: Lil Bunny
description:
I designed this pendant in December 2019.

This is dedicated to Lil Peep and Lil Tracy.

The pendant is the tattoos of two friends:
bunny - Lil Tracy's tattoo
LOVE, 11-1, broken heart and little star - Lil Peep's tattoo

I made it completely myself:
- design 
- laser cutting
- grinding and polishing of metal.

GIF made in September 2021
